OL,3,CHomes flooded and school closed after
OL,4,Cburst water pipe
OL,6,FA number of homes have been flooded
OL,7,Fand a school has closed due to a burst
OL,8,Fwater pipe.
OL,10,FResidents in Trelewis, Merthyr Tydfil,
OL,11,Fhave been affected, with Trelewis
OL,12,FCommunity Centre offering shelter for
OL,13,Fthose affected.
OL,15,FMerthyr Tydfil Council posted on X,
OL,16,Fformerly Twitter, saying: "We are
OL,17,Fworking closely with Dwr Cymru,
OL,18,FMerthyr Valley Homes and Merthyr
OL,19,FTydfil HA to support residents and are
OL,20,Fworking to resolve this as soon as
OL,21,Fpossible.
