OL,3,CHomes flooded and school closed after
OL,4,Cburst water pipe
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Dwr Cymru Welsh
OL,7,FWater said: "We're dealing with a
OL,8,Fburst water main in Trelewis which is
OL,9,Faffecting supplies to customers in
OL,10,FTrelewis and also surrounding
OL,11,Fcommunities. The burst was caused by a
OL,12,Fcontractor working in the area and our
OL,13,Fteam is on site so that we can repair
OL,14,Fthe damaged main.
OL,16,F"We know that a very small number of
OL,17,Fproperties in the immediate vicinity
OL,18,Fof the burst have been affected by the
OL,19,Fwater escaping from the damaged main.
OL,20,FWe are dealing with these residents
OL,21,Fdirectly.
