OL,3,CHomes flooded and school closed after
OL,4,Cburst water pipe
OL,6,F"We're also contacting customers on
OL,7,Four Priority Services Register to
OL,8,Fprovide them with bottled water and
OL,9,Falso be setting up bottled water
OL,10,Fstations.
OL,12,F"We would like to apologise for the
OL,13,Finconvenience caused and want to
OL,14,Fassure customers that we will repair
OL,15,Fthe pipe and restore supplies as
OL,16,Fquickly as we can.
OL,18,F"Customers can keep up to date on
OL,19,Fprogress with the repair through our
OL,20,Fsocial media and the In Your Area
OL,21,FSection of our website."
